Property CMImplPriority is a string which represents a relative implementation priority for the issue represented by this ChangeNoticeRevision object. Property CMImplPriority is a string value selected from a list of string values derived from the LOV called CM Priority with default values {1,2,3,4}. Property CMImplPriority can be used to help decide which implementations to work on first. NULL value allowed.

Property CMReason is a string which represents a description of the reason category for the existence of this ChangeRequestRevision object. Property CMReason is a string value selected from a list of string values derived from the LOV called CM CR Reason with default values {To Fix,To Prevent,To Improve}. Businesses usually can identify different types of changes (e.g. safety, performance) that they process on a regular basis and these should become the values in the LOV for this property. NULL value allowed.

Property CMTechReviewPriority is a string which represents a technical review priority for the issue represented by this ChangeRequestRevision object. Property CMTechReviewPriority is a string value selected from a list of string values derived from the LOV called CM Priority with default values {1,2,3,4}. Property CMTechReviewPriority can be used to help decide which problems to work on first. NULL value allowed.

Condition.name: SR5WF20EbomFrozen
Condition.expression: (o.object_type="SR5EngEndItemRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5EngMajorAssyRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5EngArticleRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5NonERPArticleRevision") AND (u.group_name="MCAD") AND (u.role_name="Designer" OR u.role_name="Reviewer" OR u.role_name="Approver") AND (o.last_release_status=NULL)

Condition.name: SR5WF30EbomPreRelease
Condition.expression: o.object_type="SR5EngArticleRevision" AND (u.group_name="MCAD") AND (u.role_name="Designer" OR u.role_name="Approver") AND !(Function::INLIST("SR5Status30",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status40",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status50",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status70",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status80",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status90",o.release_status_list,"name"))

Condition.name: SR5WF40EbomRelease
Condition.expression: (o.object_type="SR5EngEndItemRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5EngMajorAssyRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5EngArticleRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5NonERPArticleRevision") AND (u.group_name="MCAD") AND u.role_name="Designer" AND !(Function::INLIST("SR5Status40",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status50",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status70",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status80",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status90",o.release_status_list,"name"))

Condition.name: SR5WFAddReqDoc
Condition.expression: (o.object_type="SR5EngArticleRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5GenCatPartRevision") AND (Function::INLIST("SR5Status30",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status40",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status50",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status70",o.release_status_list,"name"))

Condition.name: SR5WFCSP
Condition.description: This condition limits the Catalog & Standard Part Request workflow to only accept Catalog & Standard Part Request Forms. The Form must have no release status and the submitter must be in either the group MCAD or ECAD with the role Designer.

Condition.name: SR5WFChangeItem
Condition.expression: ((o != null) AND u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubTypeOf(o,"ChangeItemRevision")) OR ((t != null) AND u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0isSubTypeOf (t, "ChangeItemRevision"))

Condition.name: SR5WFEditColorDefOrWeld
Condition.expression: (o.object_type="SR5ColorDefRevision" OR o.object_type="SR5WeldRevision") AND u.group_name="MDM" AND (Function::INLIST("SR5Status40",o.release_status_list,"name") OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status50",o.release_status_list,"name")) AND !Function::INLIST("SR5Status90",o.release_status_list,"name")

Condition.name: SR5WFFreezeElectricalAssembly
Condition.expression: (o.object_type = "SR5ElectricAssyRevision") AND (u.group_name = "ECAD" OR u.group_name = "Services" OR u.group_name = "dba") AND (o.last_release_status = NULL)

Condition.name: SR5WFPreReleaseElectricalAssembly
Condition.expression: (o.object_type = "SR5ElectricAssyRevision") AND (u.group_name = "ECAD" OR u.group_name = "Services" OR u.group_name = "dba") AND (o.last_release_status = NULL OR Function::INLIST("SR5Status20", o.release_status_list, "name"))

Condition.name: SR5WFReleaseColorDefinition
Condition.expression: (o.object_type="SR5ColorDefRevision" or o.object_type="SR5WeldRevision") and u.group_name="MDM" and o.last_release_status=NULL

Condition.name: SR5WFReleaseElectricalAssembly
Condition.expression: (o.object_type = "SR5ElectricAssyRevision") AND (u.group_name = "ECAD" OR u.group_name = "Services" OR u.group_name = "dba") AND (o.last_release_status = NULL)

Condition.name: SR5WFSendToE3
Condition.expression: (u.group_name = "Services" OR u.group_name = "dba") OR ((u.group_name = "MDM" OR u.group_name = "ECAD" OR u.group_name = "MCAD") AND (o.object_type = "SR5EngArticleRevision" OR o.object_type = "SR5GenCatPartRevision")) OR (o.object_type = "SR5ElectricAssyRevision" AND u.group_name = "ECAD")

TcLOVValue.description: An end item is the final product, that is, the result of the complex assembly process.
All installation kits together contain the components of a major assembly.
Major assemblies are the components of an end item and represent a large section of the product.
Raw materials are very basic materials. They are not produced by STADLER and therefore are always procured externally and then processed. Examples: steel, aluminium, etc.
Nonvaluated materials are managed on a quantity basis, but not by value. Examples: development materials, promotional materials, garbage bags, pandemic masks, paper roll, transport carton etc.
Major assemblies are the components of an end item and represent a large section of the product.

Production resources/tools are procured externally/internally and used in production or plant maintenance. A material master record of this material type can contain purchasing data, but not sales data. Example: jigs

Condition.expression: u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0isObjectTypePresentInPref( "TCCheckoutReserveOnly", o ) = false AND o.checked_out = "Y" AND u.fnd0ConditionHelper.fnd0getPropValueOnRefObj( o, "reservation", "site_reserved" ) = "false" AND ((o.checked_out_user = u.user AND o.is_modifiable = true) OR u.group_name = "dba" OR u.group_name="TC Admin")
Condition.description: This condition determines if the check-out of instances of a particular business object type can be cancelled at the current site.

Condition.name: Awp0CutCmdCond
Condition.expression: ((s.fnd0ParentSelection!=null AND s.fnd0SelectedObjects!=null AND ( u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0GetPropertyValue(o,"fnd0IsCreatedInContext","false",false) OR u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0isArrayOrRefPropertyValueEmpty(o,"fnd0ContextContrast",true) = true) AND ( u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0IsObjectType(o,"Participant")=false ))) AND ( u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0IsObjectType(o,"CATPart")=false ) AND ( u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0IsObjectType(o,"CATProduct")=false ) AND ( u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0IsObjectType(o,"CATDrawing")=false ) AND ( u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0IsObjectType(o,"CATCache")=false ) AND ( u.fnd0ConditionHelper.awp0IsObjectType(o,"catia_model_attributes")=false )
Condition.description: This condition determines if the passed, Fnd0Selection object is not null, its parent selection property is not null and fnd0IsCreatedInContext property on fnd0ContextContrast of selected objects are all set to false.

Condition.name: Fnd0AccessInboxPrivilege
Condition.description: This condition restricts an user from accessing another user's Inbox in Active Workspace client.

Condition.name: Fnd0AssignTaskPrivilege
Condition.expression: (u.group_name="TC Admin") OR (u.group_name="dba") OR (task != NULL AND ((task.owning_user=u.user) OR (task.fnd0Assignee=u.user) OR (task.active_surrogate=u.user))) OR (signoff != NULL AND (signoff.decision=0) AND ((signoff.fnd0ParentTask.owning_user=u.user) OR (signoff.fnd0ParentTask.fnd0Assignee=u.user) OR ((signoff.group_member != NULL) AND (signoff.group_member.user=u.user)) OR ((signoff.active_surrogate != NULL) AND (signoff.active_surrogate.user=u.user))))
Condition.description: This condition "Fnd0AssignTaskPrivilege" restricts the assignment of workflow task as follows. If the current user's group is dba, no further checks are made. For single user tasks the current user must be either an assignee or an active surrogate for the task. For signoff tasks the decision must not be set and the current user must be either the assigned group member or the active surrogate.
